| **Base-Height** | (base × height) / 2 | Height known |
| **Two Sides + Angle** | (a × b × sin(C)) / 2 | Angle known |
| **Coordinates** | \|x₁(y₂-y₃) + x₂(y₃-y₁) + x₃(y₁-y₂)\|/2 | Vertex coordinates |

